text = "What is PolyMesh, well this is a VR-First 3D Modeller!
Be prepared to Design, Create and bring your structures to life (Virtually) with your own hands.
This is the Manual and shall help you throughout learning this software to help you make the most out of this fantastic software!
Use either trigger to press the buttons below to continue!"
