text = "Now for the precision modelling, here you can you toggle the snap features, this will update the HUD under snap, Click the Snap Movements button and watch the HUD.
Head back to the build tab and try spawning in something you may notice the slight jolt between certain legnths, thats the snap, this works for moving, scaling and roating in the Edit script too!
