text = "This world setting allows you to see these objects and structures, in your real life environment, be ready to see your creations virtually come to life!
Click the passthrough button to start, and if you ever want to return just press the passthrough button again and you'll see the world overlay again.
Keep in mind your Camera Y axis is locked in passthrough mode, so objects will follow your eye level, this works differently in virtual mode!"
